# Redis Cache Patterns (Skill: redis-cache-patterns)

Kanonik kaynak: `.claude/skills/redis-cache-patterns/SKILL.md`

## Key Formati (Otomatik)
```
{tenantId}::{cacheName}::{key}
Ornek: tenant1::posts::42
```
`CacheConfig.computePrefixWith` otomatik tenant prefix ekler. `@Cacheable` key'ine tenant ekleme.

## TTL
- Genel: 10 dakika
- Auth cache: 30 dakika (`auth:user:{username}`, RedisTemplate ile)

## Pattern
```java
// Okuma
@Cacheable(value = "posts", key = "#id")
@Cacheable(value = "posts", key = "'paged_' + #pageable.pageNumber + '_' + #pageable.pageSize + '_' + #pageable.sort.toString()")

// Yazma/Silme — allEntries = true (list cache'ler de temizlenir, sadece o tenant'in)
@CacheEvict(value = "posts", allEntries = true)
```

## Graceful Fallback
`GracefulCacheErrorHandler` → Redis down ise `log.warn`, DB'den okumaya devam, uygulama cokmez.

## Anti-Pattern'ler
- `@Cacheable` + `@Transactional` ayni method: rollback olursa cache zehirlenir
- `@CacheEvict` olmadan `@Cacheable`: stale data
- Auth cache'ini annotation ile yonetme → `UserAuthCacheService` + RedisTemplate kullan
- Cache key'inde entity referansi kullanma → primitive/String kullan
